Package com.gpch.mongo.model

Class User

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.gpch.mongo.model.User

  • public class User
extends java.lang.Object
    Author:
    Gage Hoefer This class defines the "User" object stored as semi-persistent data in our database. The class contains all information about a user/worker that the application needs to operate.
